snippet.title: EXPLAINED: David Beckham, Qatar & the questions he has to answer | Matt Slater
snippet.description:
Joe Molloy is joined by The Athletic's Matt Slater to discuss David Beckham's recent deal to become an ambassador of Qatar, while Dan McDonnell will be discussing the League of Ireland manager merrygoround.

In association with Sky Ireland
